Package: ai.vital.vitalsigns.model

[Java] Class VITAL_GraphContainerObject

        • ai.vital.vitalsigns.model.VITAL_GraphContainerObject

        • A base class for schema-less graph objects, such as sparql results binding etc. The property values are unwrapped, it is user responsibility to make sure all objects are serializable
